## ğŸ† Why Choose PandasSchemaster?

| Feature | PandasSchemaster | Regular Pandas |
|---------|------------------|----------------|
| **Type Safety** | âœ… Compile-time column checking | âŒ Runtime string errors |
| **IDE Support** | âœ… Full autocompletion | âŒ No column suggestions |
| **Refactoring** | âœ… Safe column renaming | âŒ Manual find-replace |
| **Validation** | âœ… Automatic data validation | âŒ Manual validation required |
| **Self-Documentation** | âœ… Schema as documentation | âŒ Requires external docs |
| **Auto-Generation** | âœ… Generate schemas from data | âŒ Manual schema creation |

## Testing

The library includes comprehensive tests covering:
- Basic SchemaColumn functionality and type casting
- BaseSchema validation and column management  
- SchemaDataFrame operations and pandas compatibility
